{"tid":1919100,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[本土]解謎game: 危險人渣","createTime":"2020-03-10T14:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T21:54:44.000Z","uid":49571,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"66059adf8cd7d6535d8e9a80a5611cc372112775","tid":1919100,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PFu8iVs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPFu8iVs.jpg&h=4ff8ecbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港本土製作，有劇情有解謎，但又唔會太難#good<br />\n<br />\nAN：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.GenuineStudio.Dangerousman\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.GenuineStudio.Dangerousman&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=3fe30130\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.GenuineStudio.Dangerousman</a><br />\n<br />\niOS：<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA%E4%BA%BA%E6%B8%A3/id1476482552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259A%25AA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B8%25A3%2Fid1476482552&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=3b70a7df\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA%E4%BA%BA%E6%B8%A3/id1476482552</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Fq7zyo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Fq7zyo.jpg&h=11dcb460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官方介紹：<br />\n遊戲是一款劇情+解謎的叙事作品。<br />\n玩家會扮演案件中的死者，在經歷被殺的劇情後，案件會倒叙回若干時間之前，讓你重新認識及了解周遭的人際關係，做好選擇，然後合起雙眼祈禱能逃過被殺的結局。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lno1D0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLno1D0b.jpg&h=526ba381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wn85mdx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWn85mdx.jpg